getSiblingMolecule

public CMLMolecule getSiblingMolecule()
gets molecule context for spectrum. In simple documents we assume that molecules will occur as siblings of spectrum elements. There may be several spectrums but only one molecule is allowed.

Returns:
the sibling molecule or null.
Throws:
CMLRuntimeException - if there are duplicate sibling molecules
